---
---
<section id="features" class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-8 xl:px-30 py-10 lg:py-20">
    <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center w-full">
        <h2 class="text-center text-black text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-bold font-main leading-10 mb-4">Features That Power Your Business</h2>
        <p class="max-w-190 text-center text-black text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
            SalesZote is packed with smart, practical tools to help you sell faster, manage inventory easily and stay in control of your business every day.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mt-7">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/shopping-bag-02.svg" alt="Point of Sale">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Point of Sale</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Fast and intuitive POS that works on desktop, tablet and mobile. Ring up sales in seconds and keep the line moving.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/container.svg" alt="Inventory Management">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Smart Inventory Management</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Track stock levels in real time, receive low-stock alerts and manage multiple locations from one dashboard.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/bar-chart-10.svg" alt="Reports">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Reports and Insights</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Instant access to daily, weekly and monthly performance reports. Know what's selling, who's buying and when to restock.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/credit-card-plus.svg" alt="Payment Integration">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Payment Integration</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Accept payments the way your customers prefer. SalesZote supports M-Pesa, cash, and card payments for seamless checkout.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/users-02.svg" alt="Manage Customers">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Manage Customers</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Build better relationships with your customers. Record purchase history, track loyalty and offer personalized service.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/bank-note-01.svg" alt="Expense Tracking">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Expense and Supplier Tracking</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Keep your business profitable with tools to log expenses, manage suppliers and monitor purchasing trends.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/user-plus-01.svg" alt="Multi-User Access">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Multi-User Access</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Create roles and permissions for your team. Control who sees what and keep your data secure.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl icon-shadow">
                <img src="/images/icons/server-04.svg" alt="Cloud-Based">
            </div>
            <h6 class="self-stretch justify-start text-black text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold font-main leading-[140%]">Cloud-Based and Mobile Friendly</h6>
            <p class="self-stretch justify-start text-neutral-600 text-base font-medium font-main leading-[140%]">
                Access your business from anywhere. SalesZote works seamlessly on all devices so you're always in control.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-8 xl:px-30 pt-20 bg-[url('/images/backgrounds/bg2.svg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
        <h3 class="self-stretch text-center justify-center text-white text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-10">Simple to Learn. Powerful to Use.</h3>

        <div class="self-stretch text-center justify-center text-white text-base font-medium leading-snug mt-4">
            You don't need to be tech-savvy. SalesZote makes advanced features feel effortless, even for first-time users.
        </div>

        <div class="mt-9 flex items-center justify-center">
            <a href="https://app.saleszote.com/register" class="px-4 w-40 flex items-center justify-center py-3 rounded-lg inline-flex bg-primary-500 border-1 border-primary-500 text-white text-base font-medium font-main leading-snug">
                Get Started
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center mt-11">
            <img class="rounded-t-[10px] overflow-hidden" src="/images/screenshot1.png" alt="SalesZote screenshot">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
